            "id": 6402542,
            "title": "〈台股盤後〉挫795點摜破32000點及季線 月線長黑跌3691點回吐2月漲點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>中東情勢不明朗，台股今 (31) 日續挫，台積電最後一盤爆出萬張賣單下殺，台股下跌 795.17 點、創今年第三大跌點，摜破 32000 點跟季線關卡，收 31722.99 點，成交金額 7925 億元。</p></section><p><template id=\"P:1\"></template></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今日同時收月線，月線翻黑跌 3691 點或 10.42%，全數回吐 2 月史上最大漲點 3350.74 點，並終止月線連 3 紅。此外，台股今天收在 31722 點，已接近 3 月 9 日最低點 31529 點，清明長假前須提防跌破頸線位置。</p></section><section>\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今天各類股幾乎全盤皆墨，僅造紙和水泥類股上漲 0.68% 及 0.39%，塑膠股漲多回檔，類股跌幅重達 7.17%；集中市場漲停家數 9 家，跌停家數 16 家，上漲 137 家，下跌 897 家。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 最後一盤爆出 1.38 萬張賣單，收盤下跌 20 元或 1.1%，收今日最低 1760 元；台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>)、日月光投控 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>) 重挫 7%，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 跌逾 3%、聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>)、廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>) 等均收跌。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>高價股也成重災區，股王信驊 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5274:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5274\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5274-TW</a>) 挫 4%、股后穎崴 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6515:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6515\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6515-TW</a>) 盤中跌停打開，收跌 6.8%，光聖 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6442:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6442\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6442-TW</a>)、致茂 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2360:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2360\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2360-TW</a>)、昇達科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3491:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3491\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3491-TW</a>)、雍智科技 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6683:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6683\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6683-TW</a>) 等跌停、川湖 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2059:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2059\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2059-TW</a>)、世芯 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3661:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3661\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3661-TW</a>) 等也跌 8-9%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>族群股表現來看，IC 載板族群重挫，南電 (8056-TW)、欣興 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3037:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3037\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3037-TW</a>) 跌停，景碩 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3189:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3189\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3189-TW</a>) 跌逾 9%；記憶體指標南亞科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2408:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2408\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2408-TW</a>)、旺宏 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2360:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2360\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2360-TW</a>) 也雙雙跌停。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>不過，友達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2409:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2409\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2409-TW</a>) 收漲成為今日相對強勢的電子指標，另外，康霈 *(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6919:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6919\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6919-TW</a>) 挾新藥題材逆勢鎖漲停、台泥 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1101:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1101\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1101-TW</a>) 也漲 2%，都是今日大盤重挫下相對抗跌個股。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
